[msg TUTORIAL_MSG01 [Assist Commands]]
[s]When you are at a loss, Assist Commands can give you[n]recommendations, based on your current conditions,[n]for activities to do and Confidants to see.[n][w][e]

[msg TUTORIAL_MSG02 [Assist Commands]]
[s]Press [f 1 10 29] to open Confidant Assist to see which[n]Confidant is recommended for that time of day.[n][w][e]

[msg TUTORIAL_MSG03 [Assist Commands]]
[s]Press [f 1 10 24] to open Status Assist to see which daily[n]activity is recommended for you.[n][w][e]

[msg TUTORIAL_MSG04 [Assist Commands]]
[s]Press [f 1 10 37] to gather everyone at the hideout. Also,[n]if you have the Network Functions ON, you can use[n][f 1 10 42] to see the [clr 2]Activity Log[clr 27] of other players.[n][w][e]

